name: metadsl-all
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "metadsl" %}
{% set version = "0.4.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}-all
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/Quansight-Labs/{{ name }}/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 99721ac07cf92293fbfa4419130ec22f84e29ef7213e64243be9fc2b28dc7d61

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python

requirements:
  run:
    - metadsl-core
    - metadsl-rewrite
    - metadsl-visualize
    - metadsl-llvm

test:
  imports:
    - metadsl
    - metadsl_core
    - metadsl_visualize
    - metadsl_llvm
    - metadsl_rewrite
    - typez

outputs:
  - name: metadsl
    script: run_build_metadsl.sh  # [not win]
    script: run_build_metadsl.bat  # [win]
    requirements:
      host:
        - flit
        - python >=3.8
      run:
        - python >=3.8
        - python-igraph >=0.8.0
        - typing_extensions
        - typing_inspect
        - ipython
    test:
      imports:
        - metadsl

  - name: typez
    script: run_build_typez.sh  # [not win]
    script: run_build_typez.bat  # [win]
    requirements:
      host:
        - flit
        - python >=3.8
      run:
        - jsonschema
        - ipython
        - python >=3.8
    test:
      imports:
        - typez

  - name: metadsl-core
    script: run_build_metadsl_core.sh  # [not win]
    script: run_build_metadsl_core.bat  # [win]
    requirements:
      host:
        - flit
        - python >=3.8
      run:
        - ipython
        - metadsl
        - metadsl-rewrite
        - python >=3.8
    test:
      imports:
        - metadsl_core

  - name: metadsl-rewrite
    script: run_build_metadsl_rewrite.sh  # [not win]
    script: run_build_metadsl_rewrite.bat  # [win]
    requirements:
      host:
        - flit
        - python >=3.8
      run:
        - ipython
        - metadsl
        - python >=3.8
    test:
      imports:
        - metadsl_rewrite

  - name: metadsl-visualize
    script: run_build_metadsl_visualize.sh  # [not win]
    script: run_build_metadsl_visualize.bat  # [win]
    requirements:
      host:
        - flit
        - python >=3.8
      run:
        - black
        - ipython
        - metadsl
        - metadsl-rewrite
        - python >=3.8
        - typez
    test:
      imports:
        - metadsl_visualize

  - name: metadsl-llvm
    script: run_build_metadsl_llvm.sh  # [not win]
    script: run_build_metadsl_llvm.bat  # [win]
    requirements:
      host:
        - flit
        - python >=3.8
      run:
        - black
        - llvmlite
        - metadsl
        - metadsl-core
        - metadsl-rewrite
        - python >=3.8
        - typez
    test:
      imports:
        - metadsl_llvm
  
about:
  home: https://github.com/Quansight-Labs/metadsl
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: 'Domain Specific Languages in Python'
  description: A framework for creating domain specific language in Python.
  doc_url: https://metadsl.readthedocs.io
  dev_url: https://github.com/Quansight-Labs/metadsl

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - xmnlab
    - saulshanabrook
